    Accordion

    public abstract class AccordionBase
extends javax.faces.component.UIPanel
implements IAccordion, IceClientBehaviorHolder
    The Accordion is a container component that displays contents in a stacked format.

    For more information, see the Accordion Wiki Documentation.
